# **A gigantic Vanilla+ modpack focused on showing what Minecraft would be like if mojang really worked.**

**This was my first modpack, and is now unmaintained.**

It has more than 150 mods, all running smoothly on my semi-potato pc, i achieved this by using the fabric loader and some optimization mods. This type of thing is pretty much ignored by modpack creators.

It ran almost 100% smoothly on my pc, with these specs:
- i3 1115G4;
- 4 GB RAM;
- Intel UHD integrated graphics card;
- 256 GB SSD;
- Tested using Linux mint 22.

## WARNING:
If you created a world before a massive update, it could be corrupted if updated. It will only work if the changelog says you can update it without problems.

